                <h3 class="about">Colophon</h3> 
                <p>Built using a custom Ghost theme that I'm forever tuning. The current typography is Bebas Pro, Aktiv Grotesk, and IBM Plex Serif. Much of my thinking on typesetting comes from <a href="https://practicaltypography.com" target="_blank">Butterick's Practical Typography</a>. The <a href="{{@site.url}}/radio">Midnight Radio</a> mixes are produced with a seven-year-old version of Ableton Live, lots of reverb, cassette loops made on a <a href="https://www.boss.info/us/products/rc-30/">Boss RC 30 pedal</a>, and occasional field recordings of <a href="{{@site.url}}/destroyer-of-obstacles/">taiko drums</a> and <a href="{{@site.url}}/desire-is-a-demon/">philosophical friends</a>.</p>
